              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12949855-corey?shelf=legal-thriller-courtroom">legal-thriller-courtroom</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12949855-corey?shelf=political-thriller">political-thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12949855-corey?shelf=suspense-thriller">suspense-thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer832367730" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer270816468962786040">My 5th Grisham book! The plot held my interest from beginning to end, and was very fast paced. I had seen the movie a while back starring John Cusack, Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, and Rachel Weisz, and the book had kind of the same premise but only the book is about a lawsuit of a Tobacco company, and in the movie it&apos;s a gun manufacturer.<br/><br/>Some parts of the book were complicated and hard to follow but it still held my interest wondering what would happen next. Highly recommended to anybody who li</span>
  <span id="freeText270816468962786040" style="display:none">My 5th Grisham book! The plot held my interest from beginning to end, and was very fast paced. I had seen the movie a while back starring John Cusack, Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, and Rachel Weisz, and the book had kind of the same premise but only the book is about a lawsuit of a Tobacco company, and in the movie it's a gun manufacturer.<br /><br />Some parts of the book were complicated and hard to follow but it still held my interest wondering what would happen next. Highly recommended to anybody who likes a good legal thriller.</span>
  <a data-text-id="270816468962786040" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
